metadata.name: INTERVIEW
metadata.description:
Our neurovideo, created using the advanced neural network Stable Diffusion, is a unique piece of art. With 364 frame options, where each frame in the video is a separate, individually rendered image with an original and distinct character. The result is a breathtaking video that really stands out.

The video has been created from the original video and converted into a stunning piece of digital art, ready to be displayed in the NFT Virtual Gallery on Foundation.app. With stunning visuals and intricate detail, this neurovideo is a true masterpiece that will leave a lasting impression on viewers.
